Photographs and ephemera from a collection of vaudeville performers, acts and stage productions primarily from the American vaudeville circuit from the late 1800s and early 1900.

Handwritten on mount: Sincere regards. Faithfully Edgar Ely as The Future Dude. Edgar Ely as the Future Dude with The Baldwins

Caption on mount: Robinson and Roe. 54 West 14th St. New York

PH Coll. 583.83
